"title": "7756: preaching, content of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7756",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Preaching is centred on the nature and will of God and his claims on all people. Expressed in prophecy, declaration or teaching, it includes the proclamation of the way of salvation to unbelievers and instruction about the faith to believers.</p>\n<h2>Preaching and the revelation of God's character, word and will</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:26-Acts20:27\">ACT 20:26–20:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:1\">EXO 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:21-1Kgs12:24\">1KI 12:21–12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:1-Jer7:11\">JER 7:1–7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:3-Ezek3:4\">EZK 2:3–3:4</a></p>\n<h2>Preaching and the declaration of the gospel</h2>\n<h3>Declaring the kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14-Mark1:15\">MRK 1:14–1:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:1\">LUK 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:8\">ACT 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:25\">ACT 20:25</a></p>\n<h3>Declaring the person of Jesus Christ and his life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22\">ACT 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36-Acts10:38\">ACT 10:36–10:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:31\">ACT 28:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:19\">2CO 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Declaring the facts of the cross and the resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23-Acts2:24\">ACT 2:23–2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30\">ACT 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:39-Acts10:42\">ACT 10:39–10:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:28-Acts13:31\">ACT 13:28–13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:22-1Cor1:24\">1CO 1:22–1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:12-1Cor15:17\">1CO 15:12–15:17</a></p>\n<h3>Declaring the victory and exaltation of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:33-Acts2:35\">ACT 2:33–2:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31\">ACT 5:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18-1Pet3:22\">1PE 3:18–3:22</a></p>\n<h3>Declaring that Jesus is both Messiah (Christ) and Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:36\">ACT 2:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:5\">ACT 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:20-Acts9:22\">ACT 9:20–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">ACT 10:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:5\">ACT 18:5</a></p>\n<h3>Declaring the call to repent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:20\">ACT 26:20</a></p>\n<h3>Declaring the promise of forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38\">ACT 13:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46-Luke24:47\">LUK 24:46–24:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31\">ACT 5:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:43\">ACT 10:43</a></p>\n<h2>Preaching finds expression in the teaching of believers</h2>\n<h3>The central place of teaching in the lives of the first Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42\">ACT 2:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:2\">ACT 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:25-Acts11:26\">ACT 11:25–11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:35\">ACT 15:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:24-Acts18:26\">ACT 18:24–18:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:20\">ACT 20:20</a></p>\n<h3>Teaching from the Scriptures</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:11\">ACT 18:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:7-2Chr17:9\">2CH 17:7–17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:2-Neh8:8\">NEH 8:2–8:8</a></p>\n<h3>Teaching on how to live</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:19–28:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:20-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:20–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1-1Thess4:2\">1TH 4:1–4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:1-Titus2:15\">TIT 2:1–2:15</a></p>\n<h2>Preaching and the edification of believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:42-Acts13:43\">ACT 13:42–13:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:21-Acts14:22\">ACT 14:21–14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:2\">ACT 20:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26-1Cor14:31\">1CO 14:26–14:31</a></p>\n<h2>Preaching and the continuation of apostolic doctrine</h2>\n<h3>Preaching should be rooted in apostolic doctrine, which is to be faithfully handed on</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:2\">2TI 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:2\">1CO 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:15\">2TH 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:13-2Tim1:14\">2TI 1:13–1:14</a></p>\n<h3>Preaching that does not conform to apostolic doctrine is to be rejected</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3-1Tim1:4\">1TI 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:9\">GAL 1:6–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1-1Tim4:7\">1TI 4:1–4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:9-Titus1:14\">TIT 1:9–1:14</a></p>\n<h2>Preaching and the rejection of merely human wisdom</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:1-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:1–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18-1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:18–1:25</a></p>",
